  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StoredQuery  
    XDSRepositoryWrapper
    A wrapper class around the AJAX XDSRepository autogenerated class, to allow injecting a test double.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EbXMLBuilder
    Class to build ebXML adhering to the XDS.b registry format based upon an instance of a N4C RegistryEntry that contains the meta data for a N4C observation.
    FileMetaData  
    RegistryMetaData  
    StoredQueryFindDocuments
    Stored XDS query to find all documents related to a given person in a given time interval.
    Utility  
    XDSRegistryProxy  
    XDSRepositoryProxy
    A Java proxy that accepts raw XML messages, formatted as SOAP ebXML or Microsoft MessageBody according to the ebXML formatting as outlined by XDS.b technical framework report.
